106 His head is formed of fine gold,  
107 and pure silver are the arms and the chest,  
108 then it is of copper up to the fork;  

109 from there downwards it is all selected iron,  
110 except that the right foot is terracotta;  
111 and it stands upon that, more than upon the other, upright.

